sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Resource Owner<br/>(User's Browser)
    participant Client as Client Application<br/>(e.g. Spotify)
    participant AS as Authorization Server<br/>(e.g. Google)
    participant RS as Resource Server<br/>(e.g. Google API)

    Note over User,RS: Authorization Code Flow with PKCE (RFC 6749 + RFC 7636)

    User->>Client: Click "Sign in with Google"

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Client: PKCE Setup
        Client->>Client: Generate code_verifier (random 43-128 chars)<br/>code_challenge = BASE64URL(SHA256(code_verifier))
    end

    Client->>User: 302 Redirect to Authorization Endpoint
    Note right of Client: GET /authorize?<br/>response_type=code<br/>&client_id=spotify_abc<br/>&redirect_uri=https://spotify.com/callback<br/>&scope=openid profile email<br/>&state=xyzRandom123<br/>&code_challenge=E9Melhoa2OwvFrEMTJguCH...<br/>&code_challenge_method=S256

    User->>AS: Browser follows redirect
    AS->>User: Show login + consent screen
    User->>AS: Enter credentials + approve scopes

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note over AS: Authorization Server validates credentials
        AS->>AS: Generate authorization_code<br/>Bind to client_id, redirect_uri, code_challenge
    end

    AS->>User: 302 Redirect to redirect_uri
    Note right of AS: 302 Location: https://spotify.com/callback?<br/>code=SplxlOBeZQQYbYS6WxSbIA<br/>&state=xyzRandom123

    User->>Client: Browser follows redirect with code

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Client,AS: Back-channel (server-to-server, not visible to browser)
        Client->>AS: POST /token<br/>grant_type=authorization_code<br/>&code=SplxlOBeZQQYbYS6WxSbIA<br/>&redirect_uri=https://spotify.com/callback<br/>&client_id=spotify_abc<br/>&code_verifier=dBjftJeZ4CVP-mB92K27uhbUJU1p1r_wW1gFWFOEjXk

        AS->>AS: Verify code not expired or reused<br/>Verify redirect_uri matches<br/>Verify SHA256(code_verifier) == code_challenge
        AS-->>Client: 200 OK with tokens
        Note right of AS: access_token: eyJhbGciOiJS...<br/>token_type: Bearer<br/>expires_in: 3600<br/>refresh_token: tGzv3JOkF0XG5Qx2TlKWIA<br/>id_token: eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiJ9...
    end

    Client->>RS: GET /userinfo<br/>Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJS...
    RS-->>Client: 200 OK with user profile data

    Note over User,RS: User is now authenticated and authorized
